{"tid":926510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺浸大籌備制訂辱校罪之際，理大已經有辱校罪","createTime":"2018-12-03T13:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T02:16:00.000Z","uid":47359,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"273c2055bf2c975d293b0bb02483c66a0955882f","tid":926510,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:15:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/students.independence.union/photos/pcb.2230193960593307/2230187853927251/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstudents.independence.union%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.2230193960593307%2F2230187853927251%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=R1krSDJj3ONsglQoqLUBJRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=6fd0bb5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/students.independence.union/photos/pcb.2230193960593307/2230187853927251/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n【校園廿三條．辱校罪】<br />\n喺浸大籌備制訂辱校罪之際，理大《Regulations on Student Discipline》（1h）條已經包含辱校罪（detrimental to the reputation and wellbeing of the University）而沒有訂明最高罰則（見第（3）節）。換言之捍衛民主牆嘅被告關同學有可能被學校政治打壓終止學業。<br />\nRegulations on Student Discipline全章：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.polyu.edu.hk/&hellip;/STDHBK/Handb&hellip;/UCAL_W307-W308.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.polyu.edu.hk%2F%E2%80%A6%2FSTDHBK%2FHandb%E2%80%A6%2FUCAL_W307-W308.pdf&d=R1krSDJj3ONsglQoqLUBJRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f364180c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.polyu.edu.hk/&hellip;/STDHBK/Handb&hellip;/UCAL_W307-W308.pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Kw0D8d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Kw0D8d.png&h=0fd2d5fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbPEUGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbPEUGy.jpg&h=63d59d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4hbLOe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4hbLOe.png&h=9665ea0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13ac4fef415467d8eb765f12dcfff81b1eab7a78","tid":926510,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:18:25.000Z","msg":"都係請律師回應穩陣啲"},{"pid":"bc83c89881e3c4657c708f4afd0b620edb4678d4","tid":926510,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"13ac4fef415467d8eb765f12dcfff81b1eab7a78","tid":926510,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:18:25.000Z","msg":"都係請律師回應穩陣啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:31:02.000Z","msg":"有..."},{"pid":"576473f4b9c36dc7f9347da0b396b4c0a32bdd96","tid":926510,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc83c89881e3c4657c708f4afd0b620edb4678d4","tid":926510,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"13ac4fef415467d8eb765f12dcfff81b1eab7a78","tid":926510,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:18:25.000Z","msg":"都係請律師回應穩陣啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:31:02.000Z","msg":"有..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:44:51.000Z","msg":"我初步睇應該都係打你維護同學的言論自由<br />\n係有功唔係detrimental to the reputation of the University"},{"pid":"767831d6b63eee214d9da3b47a4484ae900d0554","tid":926510,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:46:30.000Z","msg":"加埋願意就情緖過於激動致歉<br />\n應該打得甩掛"},{"pid":"206bee54504d74b7314ecfa6805c6aae3f88db92","tid":926510,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T08:19:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3249c9b23df64b06b2a24a4f57b939d2d44e7c97","tid":926510,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"767831d6b63eee214d9da3b47a4484ae900d0554","tid":926510,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:46:30.000Z","msg":"加埋願意就情緖過於激動致歉<br />\n應該打得甩掛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T11:28:21.000Z","msg":"唔會致歉, 冇做錯"},{"pid":"428dc3590845baee4a44941e1a4e59aeb88e68c9","tid":926510,"uid":187232,"like":0,